These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, train, roller
City: miami, paris, edinburgh
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, dog, guinea-pig
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, tiparillo, ritmeester
3 different games are played: poker, bridge, chess
House: ranch-style, tower, wooden
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, october, february
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is the tower house##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is the ritmeester-smoker##1
 3. the person driving the roller is between the wooden house and the person driving the train##2
 4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the ranch-style house##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Transport      | train    | roller   | jet-ski           |
| City          | paris       | edinburgh    | miami         |
| Pet         | dog    | guinea-pig  | hedgehog        |
| Cigar           | baccarat | tiparillo   | ritmeester      |
| Game   | bridge        | chess    | poker       |
| House   | tower     | ranch-style  | wooden       |
| Birthday         | may     | october | february |

