.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, card-games, fishing
House: colonial, futuristic, palace
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil, iris
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, may, august
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, azure, chestnut
3 different games are played: bridge, canasta, poker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros, pall-mall
 1. the person playing poker is the person who likes azure##1
 2. the person playing poker is the person who growsiris##1
 3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the havana-smoker is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
 5. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 8. the colonial house is the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the person playing poker is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Hobby      | puzzles   | fishing    | card-games         |
| House          | colonial    | futuristic | palace          |
| Flower   | azalea  | iris  | daffodil     |
| Birthday   | august       | may      | june         |
| Color   | chestnut      | azure   | lilac    |
| Game           | bridge        | poker      | canasta         |
| Cigar         | oliveros | havana  | pall-mall |

