House: wooden, ranch-style, art-deco
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold, azalea
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, water
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, october, march
 1. the person playing canasta is the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the person who growsazalea is the pilot##1
 3. the aristoff-smoker is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 4. the davidoff-smoker is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the lawyer is between the person who growsmarigold and the art-deco house##2
 8. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the wooden house##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the person drinking water is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
11. the person who growsmarigold is the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Game          | mah-jongg      | canasta      | whist      |
