City: hamburg, colone, paris
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is the wooden house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
 5. the wooden house is between the craftsman house and the person who growssunflower##2
 6. the wooden house is between the art-deco house and the chaman-smoker##2
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
10. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
