3 different games are played: chess, backgammon, snooker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, old-henry, vegafina
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, country, rock
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, writer, paramedic
 1. the fan rock is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes coral is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the person who growsdahlia is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 5. the police-officer is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 6. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 7. the paramedic is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person playing chess##2
 8. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the fan indie##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is the police-officer##1
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
